OL,3,CTOWIE star Jake Hall found dead in
OL,4,CSpain
OL,6,FThe Only Way Is Essex star Jake Hall
OL,7,Fhas been found dead in Spain at the
OL,8,Fage of 35.
OL,10,FA Foreign Office spokesperson told ITV
OL,11,FNews on Thursday: "We are supporting
OL,12,Fthe family of a British man who has
OL,13,Fdied in Spain and are in contact with
OL,14,Fthe local authorities."
OL,16,FReports say the star suffered fatal
OL,17,Finjuries believed to have been caused
OL,18,Fby shards of glass, according to The
OL,19,FSun.
