OL,6,FPolice are reportedly investigating
OL,7,Fwhether he accidentally collided with
OL,8,Fa glass door.
OL,10,FHall, who ran a menswear brand, By
OL,11,FJake Hall, joined the cast of Towie in
OL,12,F2015, and dated co-star Chloe Lewis
OL,13,Fbefore quitting in 2024.
OL,15,FHe also dated Real Housewives of
OL,16,FCheshire star Misse Beqiri, with whom
OL,17,Fhe has a daughter, River, eight.
