OL,3,CTOWIE star Jake Hall found dead in
OL,4,CSpain
OL,6,FHall last posted a video on his
OL,7,FInstagram on Wednesday from Mallorca,
OL,8,Fwith a caption "Life is bol***ks
OL,9,Fsometimes but I'm gonna try remember
OL,10,Fthe good things."
OL,12,FCelebrity DJ Fat Tony paid tribute to
OL,13,Fhim, writing on Instagram:
OL,14,F"Devastating news we Love you
OL,15,F@jakehall such an awful loss to the
OL,16,Fworld you beautiful man x."
